## Overview
Unminified copy of Bootstrap v3.3.7 CSS (6757 lines). The readable, commented version of the Bootstrap framework for development inspection and debugging. The minified counterpart `bootstrap.min.css` is used in the running application.

## Interface
No exports. Reference/development file.

## Dependencies
No project-level dependencies. Vendor file.

## Implementation Notes
- Bootstrap version: 3.3.7
- 6757 lines
- Same content as `app/styles/bootstrap.css`
- Used for developer reference; `bootstrap.min.css` is loaded in production
